lead_paragraph: Travis Hamonic and John Tavares each had a goal and an assist in the third period and the New York Islanders defeated the Ottawa Senators 5-2 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Late Goals by Hamonic, Tavares Lead Isles Over Senators 5-2
